= scrollysign

== DESCRIPTION:

* github.com/mogest/scrollysign

Author:: Roger Nesbitt (roger@youdo.co.nz)
Date:: October 22, 2010
Release:: 1.0.1

This Ruby library interfaces with LED signs that use the Alpha protocol.

== EXAMPLES:

See the samples/ directory for an example of how to use scrollysign.

== INSTALL:

* sudo gem install ruby-serialport scrollysign

== REQUIREMENTS:

* Needs the ruby-serialport gem.

